===Noun===
'''localization''' (plural: '''localizations''')

#The act of [[localize|localizing]].
#The [[state]] of being localized.
#(''software engineering'') The act or process of making a product [[suitable]] for use in a particular country or [[region]], typically by [[translating]] text into the [[language]] of that country or region and, if necessary, ensuring support of non-Latin [[character set]]s.

